text: Mohamed Irfaan Ali (born 25 April 1980) is a Guyanese politician. He is the 10th President of Guyana since 2020. He was a Member of ParliamentHon. Mohamed I. Alli, MP Parliament of Guyana and the Minister of Housing. ==References== Category:1980 births Category:Living people Category:Current national leaders Category:Presidents of Guyana
title: Irfaan Ali
